{"tid":1549854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再一堆文宣圖推Post?","createTime":"2019-09-07T13:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:39:03.000Z","uid":218313,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dfbf4ee06db005efc4e6ef345babe2c41213c18f","tid":1549854,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"作為文宣組一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好明白巴絲們想盡快將文宣傳出去<br />\n<br />\n但係呢一排有太多post一連就五六張圖<br />\n燃燒數據係一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最大問題係堆文宣圖變左好似Spam咁<br />\n我依家下意識見文宣圖就飛左佢無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前呂麗巴既bot仲恐怖<br />\n想正常睇post討論係好困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我強烈建議各位巴絲<br />\n推文宣用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一張</span></span>簡而清既圖黎推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣必須要言簡意清<br />\n多係無用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n謝謝巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1989665032e74078fa5b29ec953f91e7f24f7b72","tid":1549854,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e1a9dee239f8e057bd72f2f3d93d38e9b57732","tid":1549854,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2aa9cad1b45c59120314d6a6d976040319bbfbe","tid":1549854,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1989665032e74078fa5b29ec953f91e7f24f7b72","tid":1549854,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy